
  Trevenant    Ghost Type Pokémon

  It can control trees at will. 
   It will trap people who harm 
  the forest, so they can never 
  leave. 
	Evolution Chain
      Phantump ► Trevenant

   ↞--------| STATS |--------↠ 
              hp:         85
          attack:        110
         defense:         76
  special-attack:         65
 special-defense:         82
           speed:         56

 Genus: Elder Tree Pokémon
 Happiness: 50	Pokedex ID: 709
 Base Exp: 166	Capture Rate: 60
 Height:    15	Weight: 710

 Types:
   Ghost
   Grass

 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Natural-cure:

    This Pokémon is cured of any 
  major status ailment when it 
  is switched out for another Pokémon.

  If this ability is acquired 
  during battle, the Pokémon is 
  cured upon leaving battle before 
  losing the temporary ability.

  Frisk:

    When this Pokémon enters battle, 
  it reveals an opposing Pokémon's 
  held item to all participating 
  trainers.

  In a double battle, if one 
  opponent has an item, this Pokémon 
  will Frisk that Pokémon; if both 
  have an item, it will Frisk one 
  at random.

  Harvest:

    After each turn, if the last 
  item this Pokémon consumed was 
  a Berry and it is not currently 
  holding an item, it has a 50% 
  chance of regaining that Berry, 
  or a 100% chance during strong 
  sunlight.


 Location Areas:
   Kalos route 20 area
